videos.description: Georgia Tech pushes the pace in transition and Jordan Usher delivers a bounce pass to Moses Wright for the two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Usher feeds Wright for Georgia Tech slam) 2020/02/22

videos.headline: Usher feeds Wright for Georgia Tech slam

videos.description: Michael Devoe tosses a lob to Moses Wright, who flushes home the alley-oop slam, forcing Syracuse to call a timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Georgia Tech's Wright fired up after alley-oop) 2020/02/22

videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Wright fired up after alley-oop

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Jose Alvarado can't connect on his 3-pointer, but Moses Wright flies in for the emphatic putback dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wright rocks the rim on vicious putback slam) 2020/02/22

videos.headline: Wright rocks the rim on vicious putback slam
